Help on: train

Training skills is done in guild rooms.
The train command can be used as follows:

  Command                     Explanation
  -------                     -----------
  train <skill>               Trains 1 percent of the given skill
  train <skill> to <number>   Train skill to some percentage  
  train <skill> to max        Train skill to the maximum allowed percentage on this level
  train <skill> to level      Train skill to the requirements of the next level
  train level                 Train all skills to the requirements of the next level
  
  Examples:
  train fighting to max
  train create torch to 56
  
